{"tid":1994561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"以前返學好唔開心","createTime":"2020-04-29T14:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T16:03:32.000Z","uid":66987,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d554d0206e6272db5c880c9be65d0d0b10775743","tid":1994561,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"以前返學<br />\n同學嗰陣<br />\n知道我有自閉症嘅事<br />\n於是佢哋成日都笑我<br />\n話我自閉仔<br />\n話自閉仔係社會毒瘤<br />\n仲用書包kick我<br />\n試過有一次<br />\n體育堂打籃球<br />\n佢哋專登行埋我度<br />\n一嘢車個籃球過去找度<br />\n最慘嘅係<br />\n佢哋因為偷睇我本簿見到貼左<br />\n「我要真普選」嘅貼紙<br />\n(嗰陣大約係1415年)<br />\n因為佢哋係超越左藍<br />\n仲要好紅底嗰隻<br />\n於是上通識堂嗰陣<br />\n專登喺所有人面前<br />\n話我係「暴徒」<br />\n<br />\n於是就喺畢業前嗰幾年<br />\n每日嘅通識堂<br />\n就只有佢地無理取鬧我嘅份。"},{"pid":"f2ca237da49b2b09515be674a9ebc014fb6c6a73","tid":1994561,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1538e33beae38215e406776e68d657f074c5ea73","tid":1994561,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ca237da49b2b09515be674a9ebc014fb6c6a73","tid":1994561,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"why laugh?"},{"pid":"836d966188e6d11638a024ee7abf7c8269cfeeb3","tid":1994561,"uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"如果你想講 我想繼續聽"},{"pid":"51bd41264912cefb0ee290937a7c24bf4719ed61","tid":1994561,"uid":277155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"現在好點了嗎"},{"pid":"6154a2e511b786bc5436cd33c5c3899d0b079eea","tid":1994561,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51bd41264912cefb0ee290937a